// Purpose:		Sets a reference to the receiver's CAM Protocol object.
//
// Parameters:	_camProtocol - A reference to the CAM Protocol object.
//
// Returns:		Nothing
//
// Changed On	Changed By	Reason
// ----------	----------	-------------------------------------------------------
